{"tid":1189140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你班傻鳩咁撚容易俾波台班5毛煽動反我達","createTime":"2019-06-06T16:02:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T09:21:52.000Z","uid":38604,"like":24,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a2cfc188de278b906a2ed95b314db3794191a973","tid":1189140,"uid":38604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T16:02:52.000Z","msg":"10個有9個反達post都係班台5毛撚樣開<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成班傻鳩咁撚易俾人煸動，佢班撚樣得閒就開post吹奏大陸劇同咩喜茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人唔笑狗都吠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"415bbd41eed06932f860c22f814ebce1c1c8b0d8","tid":1189140,"uid":249971,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T16:03:36.000Z","msg":"因達哥而分裂，係助長緊五毛<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1189127\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1189127</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"84961f6124ee8daac5b4e8f023211b0da1202282","tid":1189140,"uid":15323,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T16:10:00.000Z","msg":"達哥唔表態得好明顯有難言之忍<br />\n睇左好多年既兄弟點會唔知佢心意係點<br />\n而家佢擺明比人揸住痛腳，唔可以亂講野<br />\n<br />\n然後就比人有組織咁不段開post帶動言論搞分化<br />\n呢招其實係共產黨常用招數黎，可惜連登充斥住既只係一班自命不凡自以為自透世事既小學雞...<br />\n唔畫公仔畫出腸都要當人係投共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90c62b7392296bd46e527872c81c3a27b5b17c3e","tid":1189140,"uid":38604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:12:11.000Z","msg":"事實"},{"pid":"720230a0290b821a7e2e17c69758a54caa86780d","tid":1189140,"uid":40628,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T17:15:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1uYXVTx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1uYXVTx.jpg&h=4312ee21&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1aaab62663ffe61259dbbefa0a4eb948f5ffd3d1","tid":1189140,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T19:35:40.000Z",